Historical note:  This campaign was begun 2007-10-11 on Wescamp.  ESR
finished his first draft on 2007-12-04.  The campaign moved from Wescamp
to mainline on 2007-12-14 and the version was bumped to 1.0 on 2007-12-26..

This is he Wescamp changelog.  Release notes follow:

